These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-1::.
There 3 different types of food: pear, peach, lettuce
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, folk, pop
1. the fan of folk is the person eating peach##1
2. the person eating lettuce is between the fan of pop and the person eating peach##2
3. the person eating pear is on the right of the fan of disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |   3   |
| Food      | peach | lettuce | pear |
| Music-Genre   | folk     | disco    | pop   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: disaster, family, drama
The people have 3 different jobs:  coach, dressmaker, social-worker
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1
2. the social-worker is between the coach and the person watching disaster movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |       2       |       3       |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster    | drama        | family |
| Job     | dressmaker | social-worker | coach         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-3::.
There 3 different types of food: lime, potato, apricot
3 different pets are kept: dog, ferret, goldfish
1. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person eating lime##1
2. the person eating lime is between the owner of the ferret and the person eating apricot##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2     |  3  |
| Food   | potato | lime     | apricot |
| Pet        | ferret  | goldfish | dog |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-4::.
City: liverpool, nizza, hamburg
3 different pets are kept: bird, fish, goldfish
1. the person traveling to liverpool is the owner of the bird##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is between the owner of the fish and the owner of the bird##2
3. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2     |  3   |
| City   | nizza  | hamburg     | liverpool |
| Pet           | fish | goldfish | bird |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-5::.
There are 3 different nationalities: turkish, chinese, american
3 different pets are kept: chinchilla, fish, goat
1. the american is on the left of the turkish##1
2. the american is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
3. the owner of the chinchilla is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the fish##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |    3    |
| Nationality   | chinese | american     | turkish |
| Pet     | goat    | chinchilla | fish    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-6::.
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, indian
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, october, april
1. the person who's birthday is in june is between the indian and the dutch##2
2. the dutch is the person who's birthday is in october##1
3. the egyptian is on the right of the dutch##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |       3       |
| Nationality   | dutch  | egyptian   | indian        |
| Birthday         | october | june | april |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, r&b, jazz
There are 3 different nationalities: brazilian, chinese, dutch
1. the fan of jazz is on the right of the fan of country##1
2. the brazilian is between the fan of jazz and the chinese##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |
| Music-Genre          | r&b  | country  | jazz |
| Nationality   | chinese | brazilian | dutch     |

