.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, satire, western
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, almond-milk, 7up
1. the person watching satire movies is the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person drinking almond-milk is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching western movies##2
3. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching comedy movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | western   | comedy  | satire  |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | almond-milk | 7up |

