.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-9::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: action, fantasy, adventure
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
2. the person driving the bus is between the person watching adventure movies and the person driving the quad-bike##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3     |
| Movie-Genre       | adventure | action | fantasy  |
| Transport   | snowmobile    | bus        | quad-bike |

