.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-10::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  fisherman, lawyer, social-worker
House: craftsman, modern, cape-cod
1. the craftsman house is on the right of the social-worker##1
2. the lawyer is between the cape-cod house and the fisherman##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |   2    |     3     |
| Job         | social-worker | lawyer | fisherman |
| House   | cape-cod     | craftsman    | modern |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-11::.
City: miami, marseilles, nizza
There 3 different types of food: blueberry, kale, zucchini
1. the person eating zucchini is between the person traveling to marseilles and the person eating blueberry##2
2. the person traveling to nizza is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |    2     |     3     |
| City   | marseilles | miami      | nizza      |
| Food       | kale  | zucchini | blueberry |

