.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-12::.
There are 3 different nationalities: indian, british, colombian
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: parkour, rowing, skiing
1. the british is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
2. the person who's sport is skiing is between the person who's sport is parkour and the person who's sport is rowing##2
3. the indian is on the left of the british##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |    3    |
| Nationality   | indian | british   | colombian   |
| Sport         | rowing | skiing | parkour |

