The people's birthday is in 3 different months: march, january, november
1. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
2. the person who's birthday is in march is between the person drinking fanta and the person who's birthday is in november##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2   |   3    |
| Beverage   | fanta  | 7up   | juice  |
| Birthday        | january | march | november |

