3 different games are played: canasta, scrabble, billiard
1. the person playing canasta is between the mexican and the polish##2
2. the mexican is on the far left##1
3. the mexican is the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2      |    3     |
| Nationality   | mexican | egyptian   | polish   |
| Game         | billiard  | canasta | scrabble |

