.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-2-20::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, water
The people have 3 different hobbies: writing, board-games, puzzles
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
2. the person drinking tea is between the person drinking water and the person who's hobby is board-games##2
3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the right of the person drinking water##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |    3     |
| Beverage      | water | tea   | iced-tea |
| Hobby   | puzzles  | writing | board-games   |

 